            <title><![CDATA[傅明先履新浙江省纪委书记]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-10/2e3c-e3cb4c610625c3b883552a28e9407004.jpg?VersionId=QzNa.nlj7d1zpgqaZwqYxC_o36hyW7CH&amp;itok=ho72rLd7" title="日前卸任山东省委常委、烟台市委书记的傅明先，已担任浙江省委常委、省纪委书记。（互联网）" alt="日前卸任山东省委常委、烟台市委书记的傅明先，已担任浙江省委常委、省纪委书记。（互联网）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-10/2e3c-e3cb4c610625c3b883552a28e9407004.jpg?VersionId=QzNa.nlj7d1zpgqaZwqYxC_o36hyW7CH&amp;itok=ho72rLd7" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
